data.description: This 5 bed 4 bath home sits on .40 acres. This home has great outdoor entertainment areas with loads of space to run and enjoy! Inside, the kitchen is open to living area and includes an eat-in space. Separate formal dining room, or use for additional living space. Three total bedrooms upstairs which includes a primary en-suite. Lower level includes family room with wet bar, 4th bedroom and bath. Three car garage for all of your storage needs. You will love the quiet neighborhood and easy access to shopping, restaurants and major roadways for commutes.
